add_rf_device.description:
A 433 MHz device was detected via RF signal:

- **Protocol:** {protocol}
- **Model:** {model}
- **House:** {house}
- **Unit:** {unit}
- **UID:** {device_uid}

Give the device a name and click **Submit** to add it. You can also select an existing device to replace (e.g. after battery change), or check **Ignore** to hide it.
